OL,3,CChanges to data sharing planned to
OL,4,Csupport islanders with diabetes
OL,6,FThe Chair of the Primary Care Body, Dr
OL,7,FNigel Minihane, says it is about
OL,8,F"putting patients in control of their
OL,9,Fdata and who it is shared with".
OL,11,FPeople with diabetes are at higher
OL,12,Frisk of going blind, meaning retinal
OL,13,Fscreenings are offered to those aged
OL,14,F12 or over who either have type 1 or
OL,15,Ftype 2 diabetes.
OL,17,FThe screening checks the back of the
OL,18,Fpatient's eye for signs of diabetic
OL,19,Fretinopathy, which is treatable if
OL,20,Fcaught early.
